# A2A-SIN Worker — example environment configuration.
#
# Copy to .env and fill in the secrets you actually use. Only the
# variables that matter for local runs are listed here. Set-once
# deployment variables (Vercel, CI) live in the respective project
# settings and are not duplicated into this file.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PYTHONPATH — MUST be the repo root for `from worker.xxx import ...`
# to resolve during local runs. Documented in AGENTS.md.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
PYTHONPATH=.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Bridge — OpenSIN-Bridge MCP endpoint. See AGENTS.md on the canonical
# URL; localhost:7777 is the Chrome-extension side and will NOT work.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# BRIDGE_URL=https://opensin-bridge.hf.space

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Vision LLM
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-...
# NVIDIA_MODEL=meta/llama-3.2-90b-vision-instruct

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Worker-side debug tracing (opt-in, default OFF)
#
# When WORKER_DEBUG_TRACE is truthy (1/true/yes/on) every bridge call
# goes into a bounded ring buffer. If a run ends on anything other than
# a clean finish, the last 20 records are dumped as JSON for
# post-mortem inspection. See worker/debug_trace.py and
# docs/debug-tracing-worker.md.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# WORKER_DEBUG_TRACE=1
# WORKER_DEBUG_DUMP_DIR=./debug-dumps
